snippet.title: Net King's Call (Cinematic Kickstarter Trailer)
snippet.description:
Hello, 

We are Greystone Games. We've just launched the Kickstarter campaign for our hybrid Turn-Based Strategy/Real-Time Action video game Net King's Call. If you see something you like, take a look at our reward-tiers & consider pledging or sharing (or both).  

This is our cinematic trailer. Please like & share if you liked it. 

Credit: 
Narration: Connor Colquhoun (CDawgVA)
Animation/Art: Christina Locopo
Music & Sound: Chris Heins
Editing: Kevin Kershaw


Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/weaponsinc/net-kings-call


Download on itch.io: http://bit.ly/NetKingsCall 

Join us on Discord: http://bit.ly/NetKingsDiscord 

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Greystone_Games

Check out our website: https://www.greystonegames.com/ 

Thank You,
The GG team.
